'''塞西爾'''（{{lang-en|Cecil}}，2002年－2015年7月1日<ref name="The Telegraph">{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/zimbabwe/11771267/Cecil-the-lion-from-king-of-the-pride-to-the-hunters-bow.html|title=Cecil the lion: from king of the pride to the hunter's bow - Telegraph|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|accessdate=30 July 2015|archive-date=2015-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151224225501/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/africaandindianocean/zimbabwe/11771267/Cecil-the-lion-from-king-of-the-pride-to-the-hunters-bow.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>），一頭曾經在[[津巴布韋|津巴布韋]][[萬基國家公園|萬基國家公園]]生活的雄性[[非洲狮|非洲狮]]，以英裔南非礦業大亨[[塞西爾·羅德斯|塞西爾·羅德斯]]命名<ref name="nameorigin">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/cecil-lion-what-could-happen-walter-james-palmer-hunters-n400461|title=Cecil the Lion: What Could Happen to Walter James Palmer and Hunters?|access-date=2015-07-30|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205205253/https://www.nbcnews.com/news/world/cecil-lion-what-could-happen-walter-james-palmer-hunters-n400461|dead-url=no}}</ref>，早於2008年已成為[[英國|英國]][[牛津大學|牛津大學]]{{link-en|野生動物保育研究單位|Wildlife Conservation Research Unit}}的研究對象，深色{{link-en|鬃毛|mane (lion)}}為牠的識別特徵<ref name="The Telegraph"/>，科學家一直在野外追蹤牠的動態<ref name="Oxford">{{cite web|publisher=Oxford University|accessdate=July 29, 2015|title=Cecil and the conservation of lions|url=http://www.wildcru.org/|year=2015|archive-date=2010-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413084253/http://www.wildcru.org/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，直到2015年被[[战利品狩猎|战利品狩猎者]]诱杀。

== 死亡 ==
[[File:Cecil_Movement.jpg|thumb]]
2015年，塞西爾被美國籍[[牙醫|牙醫]]沃爾特·帕爾默（{{lang|en|Walter Palmer}}）射殺<ref name=BBC33699346>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-us-canada-33699346|title=Cecil the lion: Zimbabwe hunter bailed over killing|work=BBC News|accessdate=2015-07-30|archive-date=2015-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151011123019/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33699346|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於獅子在[[國家公園|國家公園]]內受到相關法例和管理人員所保護，據報沃爾特跟職業獵人西奧·布隆克霍斯特（{{lang|en|Theo Bronkhorst}}）用動物屍體作餌，將之綁在[[吉普車|吉普車]]後拖行，引誘塞西爾離開公園範圍，先用[[弓|弓]][[箭|箭]]將牠射傷<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ocregister.com/articles/palmer-674504-lion-tuesday.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-07-30 |archive-date=2017-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305234526/http://www.ocregister.com/articles/palmer-674504-lion-tuesday.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，再追蹤牠達40小時，最後用[[步槍|步槍]]將牠射死<ref name="The Telegraph"/>。死後，塞西爾慘被剝皮及割下頭顱，並且製作成標本。另外，也有人指出他們曾發現塞西爾身上的發信器並試圖破壞它<ref name=BBC33699346/>。

據津巴布韋保育工作小組稱，該獵殺屬非法行為，該名職業獵人及凶案現場的地主都沒有獵殺獅子的許可證<ref>{{Cite web|title = Killing of Cecil the Lion Sparks Debate Over Trophy Hunts|url = http://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/07/150728-cecil-lion-killing-trophy-hunting-conservation-animals|website = National Geographic News|accessdate = 2015-07-28|first = Brian Clark|last = Howard|first2 = National Geographic PUBLISHED July|last2 = 28|archive-date = 2019-07-31|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190731195723/https://news.nationalgeographic.com/2015/07/150728-cecil-lion-killing-trophy-hunting-conservation-animals/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/environment/2015/jul/28/killer-of-cecil-the-lion-was-american-zimbabwe-officials-claim|title=Killer of Cecil the lion was dentist from Minnesota, claim Zimbabwe officials|author=Ashifa Kassam|work=the Guardian|access-date=2015-07-30|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201231436/https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2015/jul/28/killer-of-cecil-the-lion-was-american-zimbabwe-officials-claim|dead-url=no}}</ref>。警方拘捕了兩名津巴布韋人<ref name="CNNMullen">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/07/29/africa/zimbabwe-cecil-the-lion-killed/|title=Two Zimbabweans granted bail in death of Cecil the lion - CNN.com|last=Jethro Mullen and Don Melvin|date=July 29, 2015|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|accessdate=29 July 2015|archive-date=2021-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210222024558/https://www.cnn.com/2015/07/29/africa/zimbabwe-cecil-the-lion-killed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由於沃爾特已經返回[[美國|美國]]，他未能受到法律的制裁。事件曝光後，他發表了聲明，聲稱自己依靠職業獵人的專業判斷，以為當時的獵殺沒有犯法。他為自己的診所不能正常-{zh-tw:營運;zh-cn:运营}-而向病人道歉，並稱打獵為“自己熱愛的興趣”<ref>{{cite news|last1=DeLong|first1=Matt|title=Read the full statement from Walter Palmer on killing of Cecil the lion|url=http://www.startribune.com/read-the-full-statement-from-walter-palmer/318947551/|work=startribune.com|date=July 29, 2015|accessdate=2015-07-30|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201231442/https://www.startribune.com/read-the-full-statement-from-walter-palmer/318947551/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 反響 ==
公眾<ref>{{cite news|title=US Man Accused in African Lion Death Thought Hunt Was Legal|url=http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/07/28/us/ap-us-zimbabwe-lion-killed-minnesota.html|work=The New York Times|agency=AP|date=July 28, 2015|accessdate=2015-07-30|archive-date=2015-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801024607/http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/2015/07/28/us/ap-us-zimbabwe-lion-killed-minnesota.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>、保育團體以至政治人物<ref>{{cite web|url=http://minnesota.cbslocal.com/2015/07/29/politicians-speak-out-on-the-death-of-cecil-the-lion/|title=Politicians Speak Out On The Death Of Cecil The Lion|work=cbslocal.com|accessdate=2015-07-30|archive-date=2015-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212001228/http://minnesota.cbslocal.com/2015/07/29/politicians-speak-out-on-the-death-of-cecil-the-lion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>對此都感到憤慨萬分。涉事的獵人及沃爾特都收到蜂擁而至的{{link-en|仇恨郵件|Hate mail}}<ref name="Hatemail">{{cite news|url=http://time.com/3977018/cecil-lion-walter-palmer-letter/|title=Cecil the Lion: Dentist Who Shot Lion Writes Letter to Patients|last=Eliana Dockterman|date=29 July 2015|work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]]|accessdate=29 July 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108132850/https://time.com/3977018/cecil-lion-walter-palmer-letter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，沃爾特在美國[[明尼蘇達州|明尼蘇達州]]的牙醫診所門前被民眾擺放一地的[[毛絨玩具|毛絨動物]]以示不滿。[[白宮|白宮]]更加收到數以十萬計的聯署簽名，希望引渡沃爾特到津巴布韋受審<ref>{{cite news|title=殺明星獅子牙醫 或引渡津巴布韋受審|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20150801/19239610?_ga=1.166526653.285461669.1438391504|work=蘋果日報|date=August 1, 2015|accessdate=2015-08-01|archive-date=2016-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813081818/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20150801/19239610?_ga=1.166526653.285461669.1438391504|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

